\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Historically called CTAs (commodity trading advisories).
 An entire type of strategies, applied using only futures (in a diversified
 portfolio).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Their advantage is trading with the most liquid contracts (passing a certain
 value threshold).
 Sometimes they use strategies like momentum (or other price-based values).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The idea is that these strategies, in general, should be 
\series bold
uncorrelated
